[{"title":"AI時代下的終端機Warp","url":"/2024/09/22/AI%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AF%E6%A9%9FWarp/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/warp.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h5 id=\"Warp是什麼\"><a href=\"#Warp是什麼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Warp是什麼 ?\"></a>Warp是什麼 ?</h5><p><a href=\"https://www.warp.dev/\">Warp</a> 是一款基於Rust的現代化AI命令列工具，內建用於命令建議和幫助的Warp AI，以及具有文字選擇和遊標定位功能的IDE。</p>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝-Ubuntu-22\"><a href=\"#下載安裝-Ubuntu-22\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝(Ubuntu-22)\"></a>下載安裝(Ubuntu-22)</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wget --content-disposition https://app.warp.dev/download\\?package\\=deb .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> dpkg -i warp-terminal_0.2024.09.10.08.02.stable.01_amd64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝-CentOS9\"><a href=\"#下載安裝-CentOS9\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝(CentOS9)\"></a>下載安裝(CentOS9)</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wget --content-disposition https://app.warp.dev/download\\?package\\=rpm .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> dnf install warp-terminal-v0.2024.09.10.08.02.stable_01-1.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"運行啟動\"><a href=\"#運行啟動\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"運行啟動\"></a>運行啟動</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 啟動Wrap</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ warp-terminal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"錯誤排除\"><a href=\"#錯誤排除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"錯誤排除\"></a>錯誤排除</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 缷載/移除Warp後先安裝依賴再重新安裝Warp</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt remove warp-terminal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝時缺少依賴套件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ apt-get install fontconfig libegl1 libwayland-client0 libwayland-egl1 libxcursor1 </span><br><span class=\"line\">\\ libxi6 libxkbcommon-x11-0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 啟動時沒有彈出Warp終端</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> apt install xdg-utils</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["終端機"],"tags":["Terminal"]},{"title":"AI程式編輯器Cursor","url":"/2024/09/23/AI%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E5%99%A8Cursor/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/cursor.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h5 id=\"Cursor是什麼\"><a href=\"#Cursor是什麼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Cursor是什麼 ?\"></a>Cursor是什麼 ?</h5><p><a href=\"https://www.cursor.com/\">Cursor</a> 是一款建立在 <a href=\"https://vscodium.com/\">VSCodium</a> 的AI程式編輯器。而 VSCodium 本身則是基於 VSCode 的開源版本，在介面操作上與 VSCode 極為相似，不需花費額外的時間適應。將AI深度整合至編輯器，內建強大的AI功能(Copilot++)，使用GPT-3.5的語言模型輔助編程，根據你的提問自動生成程式碼及提供程式碼建議。</p>\n<h5 id=\"下載並安裝Cursor\"><a href=\"#下載並安裝Cursor\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載並安裝Cursor\"></a>下載並安裝Cursor</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用套件管理工具安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install Anysphere.Cursor</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"更新Cursor版本\"><a href=\"#更新Cursor版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新Cursor版本\"></a>更新Cursor版本</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新至最新版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget upgrade Anysphere.Cursor</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Cursor"]},{"title":"VSCode Windows快捷鍵","url":"/2024/09/24/VSCode-Windows%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%8D%B5/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/vscodekeymap.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["VSCode"]},{"title":"VSCode配置PHP除錯工具XDebug","url":"/2024/09/23/VSCode%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEPHP%E9%99%A4%E9%8C%AF%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7XDebug/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/vscodexdebug.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作步驟\"><a href=\"#操作步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作步驟\"></a>操作步驟</h4><ol>\n<li>開啟 <a href=\"https://xdebug.org/wizard\">Installation Wizard</a> 頁面</li>\n<li>打開命令提示字元執行 <code>php -i | clip</code> 複製PHP信息後貼上</li>\n<li>下載Xdebug擴充模組 <a href=\"\">php_xdebug-3.3.1-8.1-vs16-nts-x86_64.dll</a></li>\n<li>移動下載完成的擴充模組至PHP安裝路徑下的ext目錄</li>\n<li>編輯PHP配置檔並加入Xdebug擴充模組</li>\n<li>編輯VSCode的PHP配置(開啟VSCode設定&#x2F;<a href=\"\">Ctrl+,</a>搜尋PHP後設置指向PHP可執行檔)</li>\n<li>使用VSCode開啟專案目錄點擊執行選擇新增組態或在除錯模式建立 <code>launch.json</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"檔案配置\"><a href=\"#檔案配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"檔案配置\"></a>檔案配置</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯PHP配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ code C:\\AppServ\\php\\php-8.1.11-nts-Win32-vs16-x64\\php.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight ini\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">[XDebug]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">zend_extension</span>=C:\\AppServ\\php\\php-<span class=\"number\">8.1</span>.<span class=\"number\">11</span>\\ext\\php_xdebug-<span class=\"number\">3.3</span>.<span class=\"number\">1</span>-<span class=\"number\">8.1</span>-vs16-nts-x<span class=\"number\">86_64</span>.dll</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">xdebug.mode</span>=debug</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">xdebug.client_port</span>=<span class=\"number\">9003</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">xdebug.start_with_request</span>=<span class=\"literal\">yes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯VSCode設定檔案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ code %USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Roaming\\Code\\User\\settings.json</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 在VSCode設定PHP可執行檔</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;php.debug.executablePath&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;C:/php/php-8.1.11-nts-Win32-vs16-x64/php.exe&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;php.validate.executablePath&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;C:/php/php-8.1.11-nts-Win32-vs16-x64/php.exe&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"檢查配置\"><a href=\"#檢查配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"檢查配置\"></a>檢查配置</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查看PHP有無配置XDebug</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ php --ri xdebug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["VSCode","PHP"]},{"title":"WSL通過導入鏡像安裝CentOS9","url":"/2024/09/22/WSL%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A5%E9%8F%A1%E5%83%8F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9DCentOS9/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/wslcentos.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載鏡像\"><a href=\"#下載鏡像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載鏡像\"></a>下載鏡像</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載CentOS9</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://github.com/mishamosher/CentOS-WSL/releases/tag/9-stream-20230626</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<!--more-->\n<h4 id=\"導入鏡像\"><a href=\"#導入鏡像\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"導入鏡像\"></a>導入鏡像</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># wsl --import &lt;DistributionName&gt; &lt;InstallLocation&gt; &lt;FileName&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wsl --import CentOS9 C:\\AppServ\\centos rootfs.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"啟動系統\"><a href=\"#啟動系統\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"啟動系統\"></a>啟動系統</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 登入系統</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wsl --distribution CentOS9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新系統</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> yum -y update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"缷載系統\"><a href=\"#缷載系統\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缷載系統\"></a>缷載系統</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 移除系統</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ wsl --unregister CentOS9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["WSL","CentOS"]},{"title":"Windows安裝PowerShell","url":"/2024/09/23/Windows%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9DPowerShell/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/powershell.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Winget(recommand)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> Microsoft.PowerShell --<span class=\"built_in\">source</span> winget</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["PowerShell"]},{"title":"Windows終端機推薦Windows Terminal","url":"/2024/09/23/Windows%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AF%E6%A9%9F%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6Windows-Terminal/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/windowsterminal.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h5 id=\"Windows-Terminal是什麼\"><a href=\"#Windows-Terminal是什麼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Windows Terminal是什麼 ?\"></a>Windows Terminal是什麼 ?</h5><p><a href=\"https://aka.ms/terminal\">Windows Terminal</a> 是一款現代化、快速、高效、功能強大且具生產力的終端應用程式，適合命令列工具和 Shell (像是命令提示字元、PowerShell 和 WSL) 的使用者。主要功能包括多個索引標籤、窗格、Unicode 和 UTF-8 字元支援、GPU 加速的文字呈現引擎，以及自訂主題、樣式和設定。</p>\n<h5 id=\"下載安裝Windows終端機\"><a href=\"#下載安裝Windows終端機\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝Windows終端機\"></a>下載安裝Windows終端機</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用套件管理工具安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> Microsoft.WindowsTerminal --accept-source-agreements</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"更新Windows終端機\"><a href=\"#更新Windows終端機\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新Windows終端機\"></a>更新Windows終端機</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新至最新版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget upgrade --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> Microsoft.WindowsTerminal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["終端機"],"tags":["Terminal"]},{"title":"使用Caddy部署Laravel框架","url":"/2024/09/24/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Caddy%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Laravel%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/caddylaravel.gif\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"快速開始\"><a href=\"#快速開始\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速開始\"></a>快速開始</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯Caddy配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor Caddyfile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">:8080 &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\troot C:\\AppServ\\caddy\\www\\laravel\\public</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tphp_fastcgi 127.0.0.1:9000</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 運行Caddy服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 運行PHP-CGI</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ php-cgi -b 127.0.0.1:9000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 訪問網站</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- http://localhost:8080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Caddy","Laravel"]},{"title":"使用Caddy部署Hexo部落格","url":"/2024/09/24/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Caddy%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Hexo%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/caddyhexo.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"生成網站的靜態頁面\"><a href=\"#生成網站的靜態頁面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"生成網站的靜態頁面\"></a>生成網站的靜態頁面</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 重新生成public目錄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"配置Caddyfile\"><a href=\"#配置Caddyfile\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置Caddyfile\"></a>配置Caddyfile</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯Caddy配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor Caddyfile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo.local &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\troot C:\\AppServ\\hexo\\blog\\public</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfile_server</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯hosts文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">sudo</span> notepad %windir%\\system32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">127.0.0.1   hexo.local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"運行Caddy服務並訪問網站\"><a href=\"#運行Caddy服務並訪問網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"運行Caddy服務並訪問網站\"></a>運行Caddy服務並訪問網站</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 運行Caddy服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 訪問網站</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://hexo.local</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Caddy","Hexo"]},{"title":"使用Hexo搭建部落格","url":"/2024/09/20/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/hexo.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝Hexo-CLI\"><a href=\"#下載安裝Hexo-CLI\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝Hexo CLI\"></a>下載安裝Hexo CLI</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Install Hexo</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"建立部落格網站\"><a href=\"#建立部落格網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立部落格網站\"></a>建立部落格網站</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># create a site</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo init C:\\hexo\\site\\blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載並設置Hexo主題\"><a href=\"#下載並設置Hexo主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載並設置Hexo主題\"></a>下載並設置Hexo主題</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 切換至blog目錄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> C:\\hexo\\site\\blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載主題</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git themes\\next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"運行Hexo服務並訪問網站\"><a href=\"#運行Hexo服務並訪問網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"運行Hexo服務並訪問網站\"></a>運行Hexo服務並訪問網站</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># start the server with debug mode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server --debug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 訪問網站</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ http://localhost:4000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Hexo"]},{"title":"使用Node Version Manager切換Node版本","url":"/2024/09/23/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Node-Version-Manager%E5%88%87%E6%8F%9BNode%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/nvm.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Winget(recommand)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install CoreyButler.NVMforWindows</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作使用\"><a href=\"#操作使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作使用\"></a>操作使用</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 列出所有可用的版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ nvm list available</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝當前最新的版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ nvm install latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝指定的版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ nvm install 20.10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 切換至指定的版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ nvm use 20.10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查看當前NVM使用的Node版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ nvm current</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["NVM","Node.js"]},{"title":"使用Starship美化命令提示字元","url":"/2024/09/22/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Starship%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%E5%AD%97%E5%85%83/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/starship.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"快速開始\"><a href=\"#快速開始\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速開始\"></a>快速開始</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載Nerd Font，確保命令提示字元的特殊字符可以被正確顯示</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://www.nerdfonts.com/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Clink</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install chrisant996.Clink</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Starship</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> Starship.Starship</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"設定Command-Prompt\"><a href=\"#設定Command-Prompt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設定Command Prompt\"></a>設定Command Prompt</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Set up command prompt to use Starship</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ code %LocalAppData%\\clink\\starship.lua</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight lua\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">load</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">io</span>.<span class=\"built_in\">popen</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;starship init cmd&#x27;</span>):<span class=\"built_in\">read</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;*a&quot;</span>))()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"設定PowerShell\"><a href=\"#設定PowerShell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設定PowerShell\"></a>設定PowerShell</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Set up PowerShell to use Starship</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ code <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Invoke-Expression (&amp;starship init powershell)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Starship"]},{"title":"使用Oh My Posh美化終端介面","url":"/2024/09/22/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Oh-My-Posh%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AF%E4%BB%8B%E9%9D%A2/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/ohmyposh.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Oh My Posh </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> JanDeDobbeleer.OhMyPosh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<!--more-->\n<h4 id=\"設置PowerShell\"><a href=\"#設置PowerShell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設置PowerShell\"></a>設置PowerShell</h4><figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查看所有可用的主題</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Get-PoshThemes</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># C:\\Users\\tpdnx\\Documents\\WindowsPowerShell\\Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$</span> notepad <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">oh-my-posh init pwsh --config &quot;$env:POSH_THEMES_PATH\\ys.omp.json&quot; | Invoke-Expression</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># reload your profile for the changes to take effect</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$</span> . <span class=\"variable\">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># C:\\Users\\tpdnx\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\oh-my-posh\\themes</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$</span> <span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"variable\">$env:POSH_THEMES_PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"設置Command-Prompt\"><a href=\"#設置Command-Prompt\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設置Command Prompt\"></a>設置Command Prompt</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 建立主題目錄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> %USERPROFILE%/Poshthemes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載主題</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl -s https://github.com/JanDeDobbeleer/oh-my-posh/releases/latest/download/themes.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 設置主題</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ notepad C:\\Users\\tpdnx\\AppData\\Local\\clink\\oh-my-posh.lua</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight lua\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">load</span>(<span class=\"built_in\">io</span>.<span class=\"built_in\">popen</span>(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;oh-my-posh init cmd --config C:/Users/tpdnx/Poshthemes/jandedobbeleer.omp.json&#x27;</span>):<span class=\"built_in\">read</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;*a&quot;</span>))()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["OhMyPosh"]},{"title":"使用WinGet工具安裝和管理應用程式","url":"/2024/09/23/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8WinGet%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/winget.webp\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Windows程式包管理器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Add-AppxPackage</span> <span class=\"literal\">-RegisterByFamilyName</span> <span class=\"literal\">-MainPackage</span> Microsoft.DesktopAppInstaller_8wekyb3d8bbwe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["WinGet"]},{"title":"使用Pathman工具管理Windows的PATH","url":"/2024/09/23/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Pathman%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86Windows%E7%9A%84PATH/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/pathman.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝-Windwos\"><a href=\"#下載安裝-Windwos\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝(Windwos)\"></a>下載安裝(Windwos)</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Windows</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl.exe -sA <span class=\"string\">&quot;MS&quot;</span> https://webinstall.dev/pathman | powershell</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Add to PATH，you can use ~ as a shortcut for %userprofile%</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> %userprofile%\\.<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>\\bin</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ move pathman.exe %userprofile%\\.<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>\\bin\\pathman.exe</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ %userprofile%\\.<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>\\bin\\pathman.exe add ~\\.<span class=\"built_in\">local</span>\\bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝-Linux-macOS\"><a href=\"#下載安裝-Linux-macOS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝(Linux&#x2F;macOS)\"></a>下載安裝(Linux&#x2F;macOS)</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux/macOS</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl -s https://webinstall.dev/pathman | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Add to PATH</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> -p ~/.local/bin</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">mv</span> ./pathman ~/.local/bin</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ pathman add ~/.local/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Pathman"]},{"title":"使用WinSW將Caddy安裝為Windows系統服務","url":"/2024/09/23/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8WinSW%E5%B0%87%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%82%BAWindows%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/winsw.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Windows Service Wrapper</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://github.com/winsw/winsw/releases</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"註冊服務\"><a href=\"#註冊服務\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"註冊服務\"></a>註冊服務</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 將winsw.exe重新命名為caddy_service.exe</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ rename winsw.exe caddy_service.exe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 建立與可執行文件同名的XML檔案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ copy nul caddy_service.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">service</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">id</span>&gt;</span>caddy<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">id</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 服務的顯示名稱 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">name</span>&gt;</span>Caddy Web Server<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">name</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 服務描述 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">description</span>&gt;</span>Caddy Web Server (https://caddyserver.com/)<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">description</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">executable</span>&gt;</span>C:\\Users\\tpdnx\\.local\\bin\\caddy.exe<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">executable</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">arguments</span>&gt;</span>run --config C:\\AppServ\\caddy\\Caddyfile<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">arguments</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">log</span> <span class=\"attr\">mode</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;roll-by-time&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">pattern</span>&gt;</span>yyyy-MM-dd<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">pattern</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">log</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">service</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy_service.exe install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"服務管理\"><a href=\"#服務管理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"服務管理\"></a>服務管理</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 運行服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy_service.exe start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 移除服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy_service.exe uninstall</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 停止服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy_service.exe stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 啟動Windows服務控制台，查看服務是否正確運行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ services.msc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 重新加載Caddy</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Caddy","WinSW"]},{"title":"使用gsudo提升Windows系統管理員權限","url":"/2024/09/23/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8gsudo%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87Windows%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%8A%E9%99%90/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/gsudo.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Winget</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> gerardog.gsudo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"操作使用\"><a href=\"#操作使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作使用\"></a>操作使用</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 取得當前終端機的系統管理員權限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ gsudo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 結束/離開/退出系統管理員權限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用管理員權限編輯hosts檔案</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ gsudo notepad %windir%\\system32\\drivers\\etc\\hosts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["gsudo"]},{"title":"安裝Caddy網頁服務器","url":"/2024/09/23/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9DCaddy%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%99%A8/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/caddy.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux/macOS</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl -sS https://webinstall.dev/caddy | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Windows</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl.exe -A MS https://webinstall.dev/caddy | powershell</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"運行服務\"><a href=\"#運行服務\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"運行服務\"></a>運行服務</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 常駐於終端運行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 後台運行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"停止服務\"><a href=\"#停止服務\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"停止服務\"></a>停止服務</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 停止Caddy服務</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ caddy stop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Caddy"]},{"title":"安裝命令行增強工具X-CMD","url":"/2024/09/22/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7X-CMD/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/xcmd.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 為Windows用戶設計的安裝/啟動模式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ curl https://get.x-cmd.com/x.bat -o xcmd.bat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux/macOS/WSL/Cygwin/Mignw/Git-Bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">eval</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(curl https://get.x-cmd.com)</span>&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Linux/macOS/WSL/Cygwin/Mignw/Git-Bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">eval</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(wget -O- https://get.x-cmd.com)</span>&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"更新版本\"><a href=\"#更新版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新版本\"></a>更新版本</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新X-CMD至最新版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ x upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["X-CMD"]},{"title":"安裝跨平台SSH客戶端Termius","url":"/2024/09/24/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E8%B7%A8%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0SSH%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B6%E7%AB%AFTermius/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/termius3.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h5 id=\"什麼是Termius\"><a href=\"#什麼是Termius\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什麼是Termius\"></a>什麼是Termius</h5><p><a href=\"https://termius.com/\">Termius</a> 是一款現代化的跨平台SSH客戶端和終端，通過在安全的SSH通道上連接到遠程服務器、虛擬機和網路設備進行管理和操作。</p>\n<h5 id=\"Termius有哪些特點\"><a href=\"#Termius有哪些特點\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Termius有哪些特點\"></a>Termius有哪些特點</h5><ul>\n<li>跨平台支持: Termius提供了Windows、macOS、Linux以及iOS和Android的客戶端。</li>\n<li>多標籤界面: 輕鬆管理多個同時連接。</li>\n<li>密鑰管理: 內建密鑰生成和管理功能，提高安全性。</li>\n<li>數據同步: 通過Termius雲服務在多個設備間同步配置。</li>\n<li>端口轉發: 支援本地和遠程端口轉發，保障數據傳輸的安全。</li>\n<li>自動化腳本: 使用SNIPPETS自動化重複的任務。</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"下載並安裝Termius\"><a href=\"#下載並安裝Termius\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載並安裝Termius\"></a>下載並安裝Termius</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 前往Termius官網下載適合你操作系統的Termius版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://www.termius.com/free-ssh-client-for-windows</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用套件管理工具Winget安裝</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget install --<span class=\"built_in\">id</span> Termius.Termius</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h5 id=\"更新Termius版本\"><a href=\"#更新Termius版本\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新Termius版本\"></a>更新Termius版本</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新至最新版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ winget upgrade Termius.Termius</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Termius"]},{"title":"安裝現代化Linux終端Wave Terminal","url":"/2024/09/25/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96Linux%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AFWave-Terminal/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/waveterminal.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h5 id=\"Wave-Terminal是什麼\"><a href=\"#Wave-Terminal是什麼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Wave Terminal是什麼 ?\"></a>Wave Terminal是什麼 ?</h5><p><a href=\"https://www.waveterm.dev/\">Wave</a> 是一款現代化、跨平台且開源的Linux終端。有著與編輯器相似的操作介面，內建Wave AI也支持Markdown、JSON文件預覽編輯，持久化SSH連接和圖片顯示等功能。</p>\n<h5 id=\"下載安裝Wave終端\"><a href=\"#下載安裝Wave終端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝Wave終端\"></a>下載安裝Wave終端</h5><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Download Wave Terminal</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">- https://www.waveterm.dev/download-beta</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h5 id=\"現代化的操作畫面\"><a href=\"#現代化的操作畫面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"現代化的操作畫面\"></a>現代化的操作畫面</h5><p><img data-src=\"/images/waveterminal2.png\"></p>\n","categories":["終端機"],"tags":["Terminal"]},{"title":"編程推薦使用的字體","url":"/2024/09/22/%E7%B7%A8%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%97%E9%AB%94/","content":"<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Fira+Code?query=fira&classification=Monospace\">Fira Code</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*M8OwSeV8gKvw1gd4.png\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p><a href=\"https://fontlibrary.org/en/font/fantasque-sans-mono\">Fantasque Sans Mono</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*ZW6aTJ6suU_5B_yV.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Inconsolata?query=inconsolata&classification=Monospace\">Inconsolata</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*M8OwSeV8gKvw1gd4.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto+Mono?query=roboto&classification=Monospace\">Roboto Mono</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*4zaS3OVdupsSkqTR.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/cascadia-code\">Cascadia Code</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*gLY8oRI0BCOO0kDI.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Comic+Neue?query=comic&classification=Display\">Comic Neue</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*6WtP2WS_KP_xex6n.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Pixelify+Sans\">Pixelify Sans</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*QHmkh_RQihg392ff.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Victor+Mono\">Victor Mono</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*x5rikYfckh7yVowE.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono\">JetBrains Mono</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*7U3LF2LA4nMe_q0o.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/noto/specimen/Noto+Sans+Mono\">Noto Sans Mono</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*L0WzHfjzA5vmYjRz.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Anonymous+Pro?query=Anon&classification=Monospace\">Anonymous Pro</a><br><img data-src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*xDVyBOf1iTI2fr5H.png\"></p>\n","categories":["其他補充"],"tags":["Fonts"]},{"title":"部署Hexo到GitHub Pages","url":"/2024/09/21/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Hexo%E5%88%B0GitHub-Pages/","content":"<p><img data-src=\"/images/hexopages.jpg\"></p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"操作步驟\"><a href=\"#操作步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作步驟\"></a>操作步驟</h4><ol>\n<li>建立一個與GitHub帳號同名的儲存庫，例如: <code>tpdnxu.github.io</code></li>\n<li>安裝部署到GitHub的相關套件</li>\n<li>修改配置文件的Deployment設定</li>\n<li>執行部署命令<!-- more --></li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"操作使用\"><a href=\"#操作使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作使用\"></a>操作使用</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Git部署套件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor _confiy.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># URL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">url:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://tpdnxu.github.io</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink:</span> <span class=\"string\">:year/:month/:day/:title/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink_defaults:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">pretty_urls:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_index:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;index.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_html:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">repo:</span> <span class=\"string\">git@github.com:tpdnxu/tpdnxu.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 直接部署檔案到GitHub，不用暫存提交</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy --generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Hexo"]}]